# üìö Electronic Story Library - Complete System Functions Breakdown

## üë¶ **STUDENT FUNCTIONS**

### **1. Student Authentication & Registration**
- **Access Code Login**: Students enter teacher-provided access codes to log in
- **First-Time Registration**: New students enter their name when using code for first time
- **Session Management**: Students stay logged in during their session
- **Profile Creation**: Automatic profile creation with access code and name
- **Login History**: System remembers student login patterns

### **2. Story Map Journey System**
- **Visual Story Map**: Students see stories arranged like a game map with connected paths
- **Progressive Unlocking**: Must complete stories in order (Easy ‚Üí Medium ‚Üí Hard)
- **Difficulty Progression**: Clear visual indicators (Green=Easy, Yellow=Medium, Red=Hard)
- **Story Status Display**: 
  - ‚úÖ Completed stories (green checkmark)
  - üîí Locked stories (gray lock icon)
  - ‚≠ê Available story (pulsing animation)
- **Journey Progress**: Visual progress bar showing completion percentage
- **Next Story Highlighting**: Current available story is highlighted and pulsing

### **3. Story Reading Experience**
- **Story Selection**: Click on available story nodes on the map
- **Story Display**: Full-screen story reading with kid-friendly fonts
- **Reading Progress**: Visual progress indicator while reading
- **Story Navigation**: Easy navigation between story sections
- **Reading Time Tracking**: System tracks how long students spend reading
- **Story Completion**: Automatic marking when student finishes reading

### **4. Form Submission System**
- **Analysis Forms**: Complete story analysis forms after reading
- **Question Types**: 
  - Short answer questions
  - Long answer questions
  - Multiple choice questions
- **Form Validation**: Required fields must be completed before submission
- **Submission Confirmation**: Clear confirmation when form is submitted
- **Progress Update**: Immediate update of story completion status
- **Next Story Unlock**: Automatic unlocking of next story in sequence

### **5. Personal Progress Tracking**
- **Stories Read Counter**: Live counter showing total stories completed
- **Forms Submitted Counter**: Live counter showing total forms submitted
- **Grade History**: View all received grades from teachers
- **Teacher Feedback**: Read comments and feedback from teachers
- **Achievement Titles**: Earn titles based on progress milestones
- **Personal Statistics**: View personal reading and submission statistics

### **6. Student Profile Management**
- **Profile View**: See personal information and progress
- **Achievement Display**: Show earned titles and badges
- **Grade History**: Complete history of all received grades
- **Progress Charts**: Visual charts showing improvement over time
- **Teacher Feedback**: Access to all teacher comments
- **Personal Analytics**: Individual performance metrics

