1. Typography Priority
Primary fonts: "Tajawal" or "Cairo" for all text (headings + body)
Remove "Baloo 2", "Fredoka", "Inter", "Nunito" references
Arabic fonts need special attention for readability
2. RTL (Right-to-Left) by Default
dir="rtl" on all pages by default
All layouts mirror: navigation, cards, progress bars flow right-to-left
Icons and arrows flip direction
